"""
    test_process_file_case_sensitive()

    This test checks that a file is processed correctly when
    case sensitivity is used.
    """
stats, freqs, top_freqs = process_file(os.path.join(docs_path, 'simple.txt'
    ), N=2, case_sensitive=True)
assert freqs['the'] == 2
assert freqs['The'] == 2
